name: Live! 3DO Magazine CD-ROM #09
overview: In this issue 3DO Magazine offers Demo versions of games: Pro Stadium, Puzzle Bobble, House Keeper ( yes, she is not released from the Humming Bird Soft !!!) and BladeForce. Alongside these titles comes movie about: D no Shokutaku: Director's Cut , AutoBahn Tokio, Ida Jiyouji Nightmare Interactive: Moon Cradle: Igyou no Hanayome, Cyberia, Princess Maker 2, NOB, Blue Forest Monogatari, Idol Mahjong Final Romance 2 Hyper Edition, Eigo de Go ! - Gateway to English, the no D Shokutaku
